like old friends,

00:27:44.135 --> 00:27:45.775
and I didn’t want to interrupt.

00:27:46.615 --> 00:27:47.615
Okay.

00:27:48.335 --> 00:27:51.535
Then I’ll finish every flavor.

00:27:51.775 --> 00:27:53.255
All of them?

00:27:59.855 --> 00:28:01.855
- This one is...
- So good.

00:28:07.295 --> 00:28:09.575
You’re eating so messily.

00:28:10.055 --> 00:28:13.015
You can slow down.
No one’s taking it from you.

00:28:13.695 --> 00:28:16.455
It’s melting, so I’m eating fast.

00:28:16.495 --> 00:28:18.175
Alright, go ahead.

00:28:18.215 --> 00:28:19.735
Thank you.

00:28:21.055 --> 00:28:22.255
This one.

00:28:25.895 --> 00:28:27.455
Sorry, Win.

00:28:27.495 --> 00:28:29.215
I’m sorry.

00:28:34.975 --> 00:28:37.615
From now on,
I’m charging you.

00:28:37.655 --> 00:28:38.975
One kiss, one thousand baht.

00:28:41.335 --> 00:28:43.095
If that’s the case,

00:28:43.775 --> 00:28:46.015
I’ll pay my whole bank account.

00:28:49.175 --> 00:28:51.135
Please, Win.

00:28:51.175 --> 00:28:53.855
Someone might see us.

00:28:54.655 --> 00:28:55.975
I can't hold back anymore.

00:28:56.015 --> 00:28:59.495
Or are you not afraid
of people seeing you with me?

00:29:02.015 --> 00:29:04.095
Getting to kiss my girlfriend

00:29:05.135 --> 00:29:06.495
makes me fearless.

00:29:09.655 --> 00:29:12.215
- Where’s my spoon?
- You dropped it.

00:29:13.295 --> 00:29:15.615
All the flavors are mixed up now.

00:29:17.055 --> 00:29:18.895
Want a new cup?
I’ll open one.

00:29:21.095 --> 00:29:23.775
- Want some?
- No, it’s okay. I’ll feed you.

00:29:24.135 --> 00:29:25.535
Alright.

00:29:26.775 --> 00:29:29.415
After this,
you still have acting class.

00:29:29.455 --> 00:29:30.575
Don’t forget.

00:29:35.175 --> 00:29:37.015
It’s really delicious.

00:29:37.295 --> 00:29:38.335
Is it good?

00:29:38.895 --> 00:29:42.015
The plane is landing.

00:29:46.415 --> 00:29:47.455
Okay.

00:29:47.455 --> 00:29:49.135
I’ll take a look.

00:29:56.655 --> 00:29:58.375
Hey, Wanneung.

00:29:58.895 --> 00:30:00.495
Why didn’t you tell me?

00:30:01.335 --> 00:30:03.415
Tell you about what,
P’Waanwaan?

00:30:04.415 --> 00:30:06.655
Don’t pretend you don’t know.

00:30:06.775 --> 00:30:07.855
Right now,

00:30:07.895 --> 00:30:11.415
the internet is full of news
that you’re living with Win.

00:30:13.215 --> 00:30:15.215
You haven’t checked X, right?

00:30:15.575 --> 00:30:18.135
But do you know
what’s even more shocking?

00:30:18.415 --> 00:30:19.535
Right now...

00:30:19.575 --> 00:30:21.575
WinMay’s fanbase

00:30:21.615 --> 00:30:24.095
is cursing you so hard
it’s trending.

00:30:24.615 --> 00:30:26.055
And you know what?

00:30:26.175 --> 00:30:27.855
Since this morning,

00:30:27.895 --> 00:30:30.015
I haven’t stopped getting calls
from reporters,

00:30:30.055 --> 00:30:31.935
my ears are about to explode.

00:30:33.815 --> 00:30:35.415
Well...

00:30:35.455 --> 00:30:36.855
Do you want to answer them yourself?

00:30:38.135 --> 00:30:39.415
Always causing trouble.

00:30:40.095 --> 00:30:41.095
Yes, P’Waanwaan.

00:30:50.695 --> 00:30:52.655
Did P’Waanwaan scold you?

00:30:53.095 --> 00:30:54.535
Yeah.

00:30:54.895 --> 00:30:56.655
What should I do?

00:30:56.695 --> 00:31:00.135
If P’Waanwaan gets upset
and tears up my contract,

00:31:00.175 --> 00:31:02.415
then my path to becoming a superstar

00:31:02.455 --> 00:31:04.975
will end
before it even begins.

00:31:05.015 --> 00:31:06.495
Actually...

00:31:06.535 --> 00:31:08.935
if P’Waanwaan tears up the contract,

00:31:08.935 --> 00:31:10.855
it might be better for you.

00:31:12.495 --> 00:31:13.695
Why, Gam?

00:31:16.375 --> 00:31:17.935
Nothing, it’s nothing.

00:31:19.175 --> 00:31:20.175
Hey.

00:31:20.215 --> 00:31:21.775
P’Waanwaan asked me
to give this to you.

00:31:22.215 --> 00:31:25.935
She said she secretly got it from the client
for our casting, so you could rehearse first.

00:31:26.335 --> 00:31:27.775
Try memorizing it.

00:31:28.575 --> 00:31:31.175
If P’Waanwaan comes back and you still can’t recite it,

00:31:31.175 --> 00:31:32.815
you’ll get scolded again.

00:31:33.495 --> 00:31:35.175
Thanks, Gam.

00:31:35.615 --> 00:31:36.615
Let’s go.

00:31:58.175 --> 00:32:01.655
But tonight
she’s going to do the same thing again.

00:32:01.655 --> 00:32:03.735
Rushing over to see
a director like P’Tong,

00:32:03.735 --> 00:32:05.135
something must be wrong.

00:32:05.135 --> 00:32:06.775
I have nothing to say to you.

00:32:06.775 --> 00:32:08.055
But I do.

00:32:22.562 --> 00:32:23.802
I told you already.

00:32:23.802 --> 00:32:26.482
There’s nothing between us.
I don’t love her.

00:32:26.562 --> 00:32:28.482
Then why are you with her?

00:32:28.602 --> 00:32:30.562
Because from the beginning I knew

00:32:30.602 --> 00:32:33.282
she could help me reach my dream.

00:32:33.282 --> 00:32:36.282
I’ll do anything to get what I want.

00:32:36.282 --> 00:32:37.402
That’s all.

00:32:37.642 --> 00:32:40.082
My dream matters most.

00:32:41.482 --> 00:32:43.162
Are you using her?

00:32:43.202 --> 00:32:44.562
If she’s smart,

00:32:44.562 --> 00:32:46.282
she’ll see through it.

00:32:46.322 --> 00:32:48.362
She wouldn’t let me
use her so easily.

00:32:48.362 --> 00:32:50.122
But if she’s stupid...

00:32:52.842 --> 00:32:53.842
P’Waanwaan.

00:32:53.842 --> 00:32:56.442
I rushed back from out of town

00:32:56.522 --> 00:32:59.002
just to deal with this news for you.

00:33:16.402 --> 00:33:18.082
Aren't you affected at all?

00:33:18.322 --> 00:33:19.882
with news like this coming out

00:33:21.682 --> 00:33:24.242
I rushed back from out of town

00:33:24.242 --> 00:33:25.762
to deal with the news for you.

00:33:26.282 --> 00:33:28.362
Reporters have been calling nonstop.

00:33:28.522 --> 00:33:29.962
Forget it, Tom.

00:33:30.242 --> 00:33:32.162
Just think of it as…

00:33:32.202 --> 00:33:34.602
building hype before the movie launches.

00:33:35.282 --> 00:33:36.922
Hype my ass.

00:33:37.722 --> 00:33:39.242
The one who should be in the news

00:33:39.282 --> 00:33:40.962
is May, not Wanneung.

00:33:41.402 --> 00:33:43.762
News like this only hurts.

00:33:43.922 --> 00:33:44.922
Oh…

00:33:46.882 --> 00:33:48.122
(Wanneung)

00:33:51.722 --> 00:33:53.042
Hello, Wanneung.

00:33:53.882 --> 00:33:56.322
Win, I just finished my acting class.

00:33:56.522 --> 00:33:58.522
Why did you finish so early today?

00:33:58.682 --> 00:34:00.922
Want me to pick you up?
We can grab something to eat.

00:34:01.042 --> 00:34:02.202
It’s okay.

00:34:02.482 --> 00:34:03.962
Actually…

00:34:04.322 --> 00:34:06.402
Gam asked me to have dinner with her.

00:34:06.442 --> 00:34:09.082
She said she’s stressed about something.

00:34:09.082 --> 00:34:11.042
So I thought I’d keep her company.

00:34:11.242 --> 00:34:12.522
Oh really?

00:34:12.602 --> 00:34:14.842
What time will you finish?
Should I pick you up?

00:34:15.322 --> 00:34:16.562
I’m not sure yet.

00:34:16.602 --> 00:34:18.802
I’ll call you later and let you know.

00:34:20.602 --> 00:34:21.962
What a pity.

00:34:21.962 --> 00:34:24.322
We won’t get to have dinner together.

00:34:25.002 --> 00:34:28.202
Then how about late- night rice porridge?

00:34:28.402 --> 00:34:29.882
Win.

00:34:31.122 --> 00:34:32.762
I should go now.

00:34:32.802 --> 00:34:33.922
I’ll call you again.

00:34:33.922 --> 00:34:35.522
Okay.

00:34:42.642 --> 00:34:44.322
I’ll hang up first.

00:34:44.842 --> 00:34:46.642
Okay, see you.

00:34:55.162 --> 00:34:56.842
Isn’t this a bit too much, Win?

00:34:57.882 --> 00:34:59.322
You’re still here?

00:34:59.522 --> 00:35:01.082
I thought you’d gone home.

00:35:01.242 --> 00:35:02.682
How could I go home?

00:35:02.842 --> 00:35:04.282
You haven’t decided yet

00:35:04.362 --> 00:35:06.322
what to do about that news.

00:35:21.482 --> 00:35:24.842
(P’Tong Director)

00:35:26.322 --> 00:35:27.522
Hello, Win.

00:35:27.562 --> 00:35:28.562
I’m here to see P’Tong.

00:35:28.602 --> 00:35:31.802
- Please go right in. He’s waiting in the room.
- Thank you.

00:35:35.042 --> 00:35:37.562
Rushing over to see
a director like P’Tong,

00:35:37.722 --> 00:35:39.362
something must be wrong.

00:35:39.642 --> 00:35:41.122
P’Waanwaan.

00:35:41.162 --> 00:35:42.402
What are you doing here?

00:35:42.602 --> 00:35:43.762
What’s strange about it?

00:35:43.802 --> 00:35:45.842
Two of my artists are in his film.

00:35:45.842 --> 00:35:47.842
I just stopped by
to talk with the director.

00:35:47.842 --> 00:35:49.122
Nothing strange about that.

00:35:49.682 --> 00:35:51.162
Then I’ll excuse myself.

00:35:51.162 --> 00:35:52.202
Wait.

00:35:53.242 --> 00:35:54.722
We haven’t talked yet, Win.

00:35:55.442 --> 00:35:57.082
I have nothing to say to you.

00:35:57.122 --> 00:35:58.402
But I do.

00:35:59.002 --> 00:36:01.402
Are you dating Wanneung?

00:36:02.562 --> 00:36:03.562
Oh.

00:36:04.042 --> 00:36:05.682
Matching rings too.

00:36:09.402 --> 00:36:11.482
Is that all you wanted to say?

00:36:11.482 --> 00:36:13.482
Come on.

00:36:13.602 --> 00:36:15.522
You could be nicer to me.

00:36:15.562 --> 00:36:18.682
I used to be your manager.

00:36:19.042 --> 00:36:20.642
A manager who betrayed

00:36:20.802 --> 00:36:22.242
and blackmailed her own artist.

00:36:22.762 --> 00:36:24.442
After what you did,

00:36:24.722 --> 00:36:26.442
you’re lucky I didn’t file a report.

00:36:26.482 --> 00:36:29.002
Then why did you try
to tear up my contract first?

00:36:29.002 --> 00:36:31.122
I had to strike back somehow.

00:36:35.162 --> 00:36:37.002
Why are you living
in the same house as Win?

00:36:37.002 --> 00:36:39.002
Because from the start

00:36:39.042 --> 00:36:41.962
I knew she could help me
reach my dream.

00:36:42.002 --> 00:36:45.442
I’ll do anything
to get what I want.

00:36:45.482 --> 00:36:46.482
That’s all.

00:36:46.682 --> 00:36:49.602
My dream matters most.

00:36:49.642 --> 00:36:52.162
What? So you’re using Win?

00:36:52.162 --> 00:36:54.962
If she’s smart enough,
she’ll see through it.

00:36:54.962 --> 00:36:57.122
She wouldn’t let me
use her that easily.

00:36:57.202 --> 00:37:00.482
But if she’s stupid,
then that’s not my problem.

00:37:01.882 --> 00:37:04.682
I never thought Wanneung
could be this vicious.

00:37:04.722 --> 00:37:07.442
With that pretty face,
I thought she was innocent.

00:37:07.762 --> 00:37:11.122
I came to warn you
because I care about you.

00:37:25.842 --> 00:37:27.162
Hey, Gam.

00:37:27.322 --> 00:37:28.682
Calm down.

00:37:29.162 --> 00:37:30.442
What’s wrong?

00:37:30.962 --> 00:37:33.322
If something’s bothering you,
you can tell me.

00:37:50.802 --> 00:37:52.962
Have you seen this clip before?

00:38:04.402 --> 00:38:06.122
I’ve only seen it briefly.

00:38:06.362 --> 00:38:08.042
I didn’t pay attention back then.

00:38:08.082 --> 00:38:09.922
I didn’t think
it was this serious.

00:38:10.122 --> 00:38:11.602
It’s serious, right?

00:38:12.762 --> 00:38:14.322
Because of this leaked clip,

00:38:14.642 --> 00:38:17.042
Win got kicked out
of the entertainment industry.

00:38:18.722 --> 00:38:20.122
Then...

00:38:21.082 --> 00:38:23.002
why are you telling me this?

00:38:28.362 --> 00:38:29.442
Gam.

00:38:29.642 --> 00:38:31.202
What’s going on?

00:38:32.162 --> 00:38:34.042
The truth is...

00:38:36.562 --> 00:38:38.602
the investors are very serious about this.

00:38:38.642 --> 00:38:39.682
About the news…

00:38:39.722 --> 00:38:41.562
There’s really nothing to it, P’Tong.

00:38:41.602 --> 00:38:43.242
I just live
in the same house as Wanneung.

00:38:43.282 --> 00:38:45.562
I don’t see what the problem is.

00:38:45.602 --> 00:38:48.402
Maybe that’s the truth,
but right now…

00:38:48.442 --> 00:38:51.322
people online
have blown it way out of proportion.

00:38:53.482 --> 00:38:54.562
Listen to me.

00:38:55.922 --> 00:38:58.722
Wanneung’s role
isn’t the lead.

00:38:58.722 --> 00:39:00.682
It’s not even a standout role.

00:39:00.682 --> 00:39:02.322
So if we replace the actress,

00:39:02.362 --> 00:39:05.002
and the film can keep moving forward, I…

00:39:05.922 --> 00:39:08.642
…I think we need to do something…
P’Tong.

00:39:15.202 --> 00:39:16.842
I’ve made my decision.

00:39:27.242 --> 00:39:28.962
The truth is…

00:39:29.802 --> 00:39:32.242
the clip isn’t
what it looks like.

00:39:34.682 --> 00:39:37.202
P’Waanwaan staged the whole thing.

00:39:38.162 --> 00:39:41.362
Because she was angry
Win wanted to cancel the contract.

00:39:43.682 --> 00:39:44.882
No wonder.

00:39:44.882 --> 00:39:46.322
So that’s why.

00:39:46.722 --> 00:39:50.722
Win got so upset
when she found out

00:39:52.642 --> 00:39:55.722
I signed with P’Waanwaan.

00:39:58.362 --> 00:40:02.242
But tonight
she’s going to do the same thing again.

00:40:02.882 --> 00:40:06.362
She’ll do to May
what she did to Win.

00:40:07.642 --> 00:40:09.922
She wants to push me

00:40:10.242 --> 00:40:13.922
to become the female lead
in this film instead.

00:40:14.162 --> 00:40:15.562
Is it tonight, Gam?

00:40:16.082 --> 00:40:18.602
- Where?
- At P’Waanwaan’s condo.

00:40:18.642 --> 00:40:20.042
Eight o’clock.

00:40:21.682 --> 00:40:23.362
Gam, send me the location.

00:40:23.402 --> 00:40:24.482
Okay, okay.

00:40:24.482 --> 00:40:25.962
And the room number too.

00:40:29.362 --> 00:40:30.922
Could you go a little faster, driver?

00:40:31.962 --> 00:40:33.202
Thank you.

00:40:34.802 --> 00:40:36.042
Thank you.

00:41:00.882 --> 00:41:04.082
Whenever something urgent happens,
you never answer my calls, Win.

00:41:08.482 --> 00:41:09.922
Meedee.

00:41:15.362 --> 00:41:16.562
Hello, Meedee.

00:41:16.602 --> 00:41:18.162
I need your help.

00:41:18.642 --> 00:41:20.442
Send me the location right now.

00:41:20.922 --> 00:41:23.202
And don’t go in yet.
Wait for me.

00:41:57.842 --> 00:42:01.042
She can help me reach my dream.

00:42:01.082 --> 00:42:04.442
I’ll do anything
to get what I want.

00:42:04.482 --> 00:42:05.682
That’s all.

00:42:05.722 --> 00:42:09.242
My dream matters most.

00:42:17.682 --> 00:42:20.122
Without a keycard,
you really can’t go up.

00:42:20.242 --> 00:42:22.482
Please, could you help me?

00:42:23.722 --> 00:42:24.762
Please.

00:42:28.842 --> 00:42:31.682
Do you know P’Waanwaan?

00:42:32.362 --> 00:42:35.042
Yes, I do.
She’s an artist manager, right?

00:42:35.082 --> 00:42:36.122
Yes.

00:42:36.122 --> 00:42:38.642
I’m an actress.
Look at my face.

00:42:41.562 --> 00:42:44.162
P’Waanwaan isn’t feeling well.
She called me to help.

00:42:44.202 --> 00:42:45.842
Please let me go up.

00:42:46.042 --> 00:42:47.682
I need to check on her.

00:42:48.722 --> 00:42:50.762
You can come up with me.

00:42:54.322 --> 00:42:55.642
Trust me.

00:42:55.682 --> 00:42:58.842
If something happens to her,
you’ll be in trouble.

00:43:00.762 --> 00:43:02.322
Hurry.

00:43:02.322 --> 00:43:03.682
Please.

00:43:04.002 --> 00:43:05.242
Please.

00:43:08.882 --> 00:43:09.962
Miss,

00:43:09.962 --> 00:43:11.642
please calm down.

00:43:11.682 --> 00:43:13.082
Wait for me.

00:43:20.002 --> 00:43:21.242
What’s wrong?

00:43:21.562 --> 00:43:23.002
Ring the bell.

00:43:34.002 --> 00:43:35.042
Wanneung?

00:43:36.122 --> 00:43:37.402
What are you doing here?

00:43:39.602 --> 00:43:41.762
I’ll take my leave then,
P’Waanwaan.

00:43:46.442 --> 00:43:50.002
She said you weren’t feeling well,

00:43:50.042 --> 00:43:52.002
so you called her to come here.

00:43:57.002 --> 00:43:58.042
Wanneung.

00:43:58.042 --> 00:43:59.042
Wanneung.

00:43:59.122 --> 00:44:00.962
Stop, Wanneung.

00:44:05.842 --> 00:44:06.842
May.

00:44:07.002 --> 00:44:08.162
May.

00:44:11.202 --> 00:44:13.202
P’Waanwaan, what did you do to her?

00:44:13.322 --> 00:44:14.322
Do what?

00:44:14.522 --> 00:44:17.402
She was stressed because of the news,
so she came to talk to me.

00:44:17.642 --> 00:44:20.242
We had a few drinks, she got drunk
and fell asleep like you see.

00:44:20.282 --> 00:44:24.202
You’re lying. You’re doing to May
the same thing you did to Win, right?

00:44:24.242 --> 00:44:25.802
What is she talking about?

00:44:27.762 --> 00:44:29.042
- Wanneung
- Meedee

00:44:29.082 --> 00:44:30.562
I told you to wait.
Why didn’t you?

00:44:30.602 --> 00:44:32.402
Because you were late.

00:44:33.162 --> 00:44:34.162
May.

00:44:38.402 --> 00:44:39.962
This is my room,

00:44:40.002 --> 00:44:42.162
not some marketplace.

00:44:42.562 --> 00:44:43.802
If you leak May’s clip

00:44:43.802 --> 00:44:45.082
like you did with Win,

00:44:45.082 --> 00:44:46.122
you’ll be in big trouble.

00:44:46.402 --> 00:44:49.242
Don’t you know how powerful
Meedee’s father is?

00:45:09.322 --> 00:45:11.322
I would like to withdraw
from this film.

00:45:11.322 --> 00:45:13.042
Then all the news will end.

00:45:13.042 --> 00:45:15.602
But I ask that Wanneung
can continue acting in this film.

00:45:15.722 --> 00:45:16.842
Wanneung...

00:45:17.202 --> 00:45:19.322
must be very important to you.

00:45:32.302 --> 00:45:34.782
(Wellness Medical Hospital)

00:45:55.822 --> 00:45:57.622
Honestly, Wanneung.

00:45:58.342 --> 00:46:00.462
I told you to wait.
Why didn’t you?

00:46:01.102 --> 00:46:03.222
I was worried about May.

00:46:03.222 --> 00:46:05.102
I was afraid something
might happen to her.

00:46:05.462 --> 00:46:06.862
Why are you worried about her?

00:46:06.862 --> 00:46:08.102
Are you two close?

00:46:09.982 --> 00:46:11.182
Well…

00:46:11.302 --> 00:46:13.062
Not really.

00:46:13.502 --> 00:46:14.502
But...

00:46:14.542 --> 00:46:15.862
But what?

00:46:17.462 --> 00:46:20.662
I feel kind of guilty toward her.

00:46:20.862 --> 00:46:24.302
It feels like I stole
the person she loves.

00:46:25.462 --> 00:46:27.862
I'm sorry, Meedee.

00:46:29.102 --> 00:46:31.302
That's so like you, Wanneung.

00:46:31.502 --> 00:46:34.062
Doing something crazy like this.

00:47:24.942 --> 00:47:26.502
Where did she go?

00:47:38.302 --> 00:47:39.462
You...

00:47:40.382 --> 00:47:41.582
Sit up slowly.

00:47:45.302 --> 00:47:46.382
I...

00:47:46.422 --> 00:47:48.102
How did I end up here?

00:47:49.302 --> 00:47:51.382
You were probably drugged
and passed out.

00:47:51.902 --> 00:47:54.942
Wanneung was the one
who got you out of your manager's condo.

00:47:56.102 --> 00:47:57.502
P'Waanwaan...

00:47:59.142 --> 00:48:01.582
She called me to talk about the news.

00:48:02.222 --> 00:48:04.942
Then she gave me something to drink.

00:48:04.982 --> 00:48:07.022
After that, I remember nothing.

00:48:07.662 --> 00:48:08.902
Could it be...

00:48:08.982 --> 00:48:11.502
she tried to do to me
what she did to Win?

00:48:12.462 --> 00:48:14.062
Wanneung said the same thing.

00:48:15.502 --> 00:48:16.862
But don't worry.

00:48:17.462 --> 00:48:20.022
My father has already handled everything.

00:48:20.622 --> 00:48:21.662
Why?

00:48:21.982 --> 00:48:24.222
Is your father that powerful?

00:48:24.462 --> 00:48:25.502
Yes.

00:48:30.142 --> 00:48:31.142
And...

00:48:31.142 --> 00:48:33.302
what does that supporting actress
have to do with this?

00:48:33.902 --> 00:48:36.062
That's just how Wanneung is.

00:48:36.182 --> 00:48:37.822
She likes helping people.

00:48:37.862 --> 00:48:39.462
She believes in justice.

00:48:40.822 --> 00:48:41.862
How annoying.

00:48:41.902 --> 00:48:43.142
Praising her won't help.

00:48:43.222 --> 00:48:45.142
She'll never turn around
and like you.

00:48:45.182 --> 00:48:47.542
Yeah, I know.

00:48:47.662 --> 00:48:49.622
You should thank her instead.

00:48:49.982 --> 00:48:52.382
If Wanneung hadn't gone
to help you,

00:48:52.422 --> 00:48:54.382
you definitely wouldn't have made it.

00:48:56.582 --> 00:48:57.742
What about you?

00:48:57.782 --> 00:48:59.222
Why did you help me?

00:48:59.422 --> 00:49:00.702
Didn't you say...

00:49:00.942 --> 00:49:02.862
we were just
a one- night stand?

00:49:07.702 --> 00:49:09.422
If I see someone in trouble,

00:49:09.502 --> 00:49:11.182
I'll help them.

00:49:11.822 --> 00:49:13.782
Don't get the wrong idea.

00:49:16.342 --> 00:49:18.982
If you're worried,
just say you're worried.

00:49:19.102 --> 00:49:21.262
Why do you have to act tough?

00:50:02.742 --> 00:50:03.982
Wanneung.

00:50:06.222 --> 00:50:07.502
Wanneung.

00:50:13.982 --> 00:50:16.342
Win, you're back?

00:50:16.382 --> 00:50:19.862
I called you so many times,
but you never answered.

00:50:20.262 --> 00:50:22.182
I went to talk with P’Tong today.

00:50:22.262 --> 00:50:24.182
I had something important to deal with,

00:50:24.742 --> 00:50:26.862
so I didn't want to answer yet.

00:50:27.142 --> 00:50:28.262
P’Tong the film director?

00:50:28.302 --> 00:50:29.662
What did you talk about?

00:50:34.862 --> 00:50:35.902
By the way, Win.

00:50:35.902 --> 00:50:38.062
I just helped May earlier.

00:50:40.582 --> 00:50:42.182
This is our time.

00:50:42.622 --> 00:50:44.182
Let's not talk about other people.

00:50:46.422 --> 00:50:48.822
If not about other people, then...

00:50:48.982 --> 00:50:50.542
what do you want to do?

00:50:56.462 --> 00:50:57.622
Win.

00:50:57.622 --> 00:50:59.102
You're getting a call.

00:51:02.542 --> 00:51:03.982
I'll answer it later.

00:51:07.942 --> 00:51:09.342
Win.

00:51:12.542 --> 00:51:13.862
Win.

00:51:41.422 --> 00:51:42.742
Hello, Meedee.

00:51:42.862 --> 00:51:44.702
Wanneung, something happened.

00:51:44.742 --> 00:51:47.782
May asked me to tell you
to check Win's Facebook.

00:51:49.462 --> 00:51:50.542
Okay, okay.

00:51:58.182 --> 00:52:00.382
I would like to announce
my retirement from the entertainment industry

00:52:00.422 --> 00:52:02.622
by withdrawing from the film
I was cast in,

00:52:02.662 --> 00:52:05.862
and I am willing to pay
all damages according to the contract.

00:52:08.062 --> 00:52:10.942
I would like to thank all my fans
for your support.

00:52:10.982 --> 00:52:13.102
and for always supporting me.

00:52:14.982 --> 00:52:16.422
Thank you.

00:52:28.022 --> 00:52:29.222
What did you say?

00:52:29.222 --> 00:52:30.942
Say that again.

00:52:32.262 --> 00:52:34.662
I would like to withdraw
from this film.

00:52:34.942 --> 00:52:36.422
Then all the news will end.

00:52:37.182 --> 00:52:40.022
But I ask that Wanneung
can continue acting in this film.

00:52:41.182 --> 00:52:43.822
Win, you've already signed the contract.

00:52:43.822 --> 00:52:45.382
There is also a penalty.

00:52:45.422 --> 00:52:48.422
And most importantly,
we're about to start filming.

00:52:49.742 --> 00:52:51.702
I'm sorry, P'Tong.

00:52:51.742 --> 00:52:53.822
for always causing you trouble.

00:52:57.982 --> 00:52:59.742
But I've thought this through.

00:53:00.382 --> 00:53:03.342
If I withdraw,
everything will end.

00:53:03.622 --> 00:53:06.742
As for the penalty,
please don't worry. I can pay it.

00:53:07.942 --> 00:53:10.982
But I ask that Wanneung
can continue acting in this film.

00:53:11.542 --> 00:53:14.342
This film really means
a lot to Wanneung.

00:53:18.542 --> 00:53:19.662
Wanneung...

00:53:20.382 --> 00:53:22.542
must be very important to you.

00:53:23.862 --> 00:53:25.942
For you to give up
everything like this.

00:54:00.382 --> 00:54:02.622
What exactly happened?

00:54:10.422 --> 00:54:12.262
(P'Waanwaan)

00:54:14.982 --> 00:54:16.182
Hello.

00:54:16.382 --> 00:54:18.382
Wanneung, just you wait.

00:54:18.382 --> 00:54:21.062
How could you do this to me,
you ungrateful person?

00:54:21.302 --> 00:54:22.782
You sent someone to attack me.

00:54:22.822 --> 00:54:24.302
What did Meedee's father do to you?

00:54:24.342 --> 00:54:26.022
What happened?

00:54:26.262 --> 00:54:28.502
- P'Waanwaan
- Don't meddle in my business.

00:54:28.542 --> 00:54:29.662
Worry about yourself.

00:54:29.702 --> 00:54:32.582
Now Win believes
you never truly loved her.

00:54:32.622 --> 00:54:33.982
You only wanted the benefits.

00:54:34.262 --> 00:54:35.422
Win is stupid.

00:54:35.462 --> 00:54:37.262
She believed the audio clip

00:54:37.262 --> 00:54:38.302
I edited was real.

00:54:39.982 --> 00:54:41.062
Don't!

00:54:41.062 --> 00:54:42.062
P'Waanwaan!

00:54:42.102 --> 00:54:44.502
Sis! Sis! Sis!

00:57:49.622 --> 00:57:51.822
How could you run off
on a trip alone like this?

00:57:51.822 --> 00:57:53.102
I won't accept that.

00:57:53.102 --> 00:57:56.942
Someone like you would never date anyone
just for benefits, right?

00:57:57.262 --> 00:57:58.982
Win Pawee.

00:57:59.022 --> 00:58:01.662
We'll hold hands like this
and walk forward together.

00:58:01.662 --> 00:58:02.982
You'll never fall.

00:58:03.022 --> 00:58:04.742
Because I'll always
be there to support you.

00:58:04.742 --> 00:58:06.382
Whenever you turn around,

00:58:06.382 --> 00:58:07.542
you'll always find me.

00:58:07.542 --> 00:58:10.302
If becoming a superstar
is my dream,

00:58:10.302 --> 00:58:10.782
then you

00:58:10.782 --> 00:58:12.422
are something even more precious than that.

00:58:12.422 --> 00:58:13.742
Believe me,

00:58:13.742 --> 00:58:17.102
you'll be my present
and my future.

00:58:17.342 --> 00:58:18.382
Win.

00:58:19.702 --> 00:58:21.742
- Oh, just now...
- That wasn't good.

00:58:21.982 --> 00:58:24.622
The moment it stuck on...
Oops, it went through.

00:58:30.942 --> 00:58:33.102
- You're late.
- All done.

00:58:33.942 --> 00:58:35.742
She wouldn't stop kissing me.

00:58:37.382 --> 00:58:38.622
(Too shy)

00:58:41.982 --> 00:58:43.262
Win.

00:58:43.302 --> 00:58:44.302
Cut.

00:58:44.422 --> 00:58:46.142
Good thing I didn't shower this morning.